@startuml
title AD-02: Dashboard Asset View and Listing (Swimlane Diagram)

|User|
start
:Enter credentials;

|System|
:Receive login credentials;
:Validate credentials;

if () then ([valid])
    :Determine user role;
    :Load role-specific dashboard;
    :Retrieve asset list;
    :Display asset table;
else ([invalid])
    :Display authentication error;
    stop
endif

' ---------- DASHBOARD ASSET LISTING ----------
|User|
:Scroll asset table;

|System|
:Render visible asset entries;

|User|
:Select Show More Assets;

|System|
:Retrieve additional assets;
:Append assets to table;
:Update dashboard view;

stop
@enduml
